---
model: gemini-1.5-flash
config:
  temperature: 0.7
  responseMimeType: application/json
input:
  schema:
    type: object
    properties:
      topic:
        type: string
        description: The subject matter for the flashcards.
      language:
        type: string
        description: The target language to translate the English phrases into.
    required: [topic, language]
---
You are an expert language teacher.
Generate a JSON flashcard deck about "{{topic}}" in "{{language}}".
The JSON MUST have the following structure:
{
   "title": "A catchy title describing the theme",
   "items": [
      { "front": "English phrase", "back": "Translation in {{language}}" },
      { "front": "Another phrase", "back": "Translation" }
   ]
}
Return ONLY valid JSON without markdown ticks. 
Generate precisely 5 items.
